replies.body:
I can't help but feel annoyed at the amount of people who make specific requests to dArtagnan about checking their profiles for bans and then proceed to badmouth Riot for not understanding their situation or caring about their efforts if they get a negative response...

I mean, dArtagnan's taking the time to check on the individual data, so I just can't help but think that it deserves at least a little respect, even if you don't like the result.
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}
